---

## Engineering Challenges Encountered

During development several real-world engineering issues were encountered and resolved:

- Docker volume mounting issues
- Airflow DAG import errors
- Container networking and hostname resolution issues
- Schema mismatches between source data and PostgreSQL
- Memory constraints when processing large Parquet files
- Configuration management across containers

These challenges provided practical experience with debugging distributed data workflows and containerised applications.

